{"tid":1023400,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"作為一個環保人士 今日比我發現大家樂既員工用飲管飲野","createTime":"2019-02-15T17:43:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-16T04:11:04.000Z","uid":231293,"like":3,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df689e7f2b1cffd646f2ac336ce92b8ebfc421c2","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:43:57.000Z","msg":"自從聯合一班志同道合既朋友<br />\n<br />\n去聯署走飲管計劃後<br />\n<br />\n到今日先第一次出街食D平民既垃圾餐廳 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁今日就去左大家樂<br />\n<br />\n順便視察下係咪真係唔派飲管<br />\n<br />\n如果仲夠膽派 一定即場屌柒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正當我行完一圈<br />\n<br />\n見到無人有飲管既時候<br />\n<br />\n我望到廚房入面個燒味佬居然用飲管係到飲凍啡<br />\n<br />\n我即刻火都黎埋<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母<br />\n<br />\n依加講明全面走飲管<br />\n<br />\n點解仲要用?<br />\n<br />\n係咪想D海龜死撚晒先安樂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我即刻當住佢面屌柒佢<br />\n<br />\n質問佢<br />\n<br />\n點解你可以用飲管?<br />\n呢到應該全面禁飲管架喎<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後個燒味佬即刻眼濕濕頭DUPDUP咁講左句 「對唔住 下次唔會用」 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我覺得自己做左件好有意義既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7635ea49c0ef06e3875f1204c1c35e9f3e0015e0","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:44:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34254cd111ee973817f298acb9eaf3765c8c060","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:44:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f24a143e695ad5bdd6cfdc44e21bc5b44e9ae1e","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:45:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家見到班用飲管既人<br />\n<br />\n一定要開聲屌鳩佢地<br />\n<br />\n話比佢地聽飲管係唔環保架"},{"pid":"2b40fafe2803d3965350c437f59599de22df878e","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:45:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"393d07446686d9fc79d15cecb10400737ab4efb2","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:46:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c006f34866e38b9cf850b59a6a280cc5182c95a8","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead77aa6a5ccd10572fbe43cd3bebbde676788b0","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:48:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f3c12e1418236785749b15f6931555643bc48db","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:48:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02393c075292a44419e31106e57cfae3588a8c97","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:49:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"201b75a7509d5e437f45d894d323c2199d5aec96","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:50:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af65be90a18b0f871489305da765f8af62a0a8b","tid":1023400,"uid":231293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-15T17:50:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8faa100b396cd0917948715b6b5c5b747af7e276","tid":10234